Yave nguva ikozvino kuti shanduro dzeKrita dzatinoshandisa pamakomputa dzinoramba dzichitevera zvisirizvo. Kubva pane imwe pfungwa shanduro iwe unoenda kune imwe iyo inoratidzika kuti vakanganwa imwe, asi hazvina kudaro. Kunyangwe ndakanga ndisati ndazvipa kukosha, nhasi, nekuburitswa kwe Krita 5.0.5, KDE atsanangura nei izvi zvichiitika: vangada kuenderera mberi neakaunti, asi Krita iri muzvitoro zvakasiyana-siyana zvesoftware uye vamwe vacho, kana vasingabvumi shanduro, vanomanikidza chinhu ch
... 
pa mifananidzo kana kurekodha.
- Kuvandudzwa kwekuona kweakatyoka mavhidhiyo akateedzana kana uchiaunza seanimation.
- Yakagadzirisa nyaya uko asiri ese mapikseli akakopwa pakukopa mask.
- Kugona kuchengetedza uye kurodha gradients munzvimbo dzisiri dzeUTF8.
- Yakagadziriswa nyaya ine masiki uye akaturikidzana achiputsika mushure mekuchinja nzvimbo yemavara.
- Gadziridza kuLittleCMS 2.13.1 kugadzirisa greyscale color space bug uye gadzirisa kushandura pakati pe8-bit uye 16-bit grayscale mifanani
...
iswa bhurashi rondedzero yekuvandudza kana uchichinja preset kana chishandiso.
- Mabatirwo akavandudzwa ezvidhori zvidhori zvemafaera.

Hongu, mabhugi mazhinji akagadziriswa, asi iyo inotevera vhezheni yakatotarisirwa kuve Krita 5.1. Krita 5.0.5 kare inowanikwa kubva website yepamutemo muchimiro cheAppImage. Kune zvakare repository yeDebian-based system ipapo, uye iyo yekuvandudza ichaonekwa paFlathub munguva pfupi.

FRP nesefa rudzi rweplate-yakaumbwa zvinhu ine nzvimbo zhinji, iyo inogadzirwa negirazi faibha sechinhu chinosimbisa, unsaturated polyester resin seye chizvaro, uye yakakosha kugadzirisa komputa. FRP nesefa inogona kushandiswa seyakaumbwa zvinhu. Inoshandiswa sepasi, pevhu chifukidziro, matunhu emutaundi dziva kabati, chikuva, chikepe dhizaini, masitepisi, plank mugwagwa, nezvimwe zvinokanganisa nharaunda. Ngura inodzivirira, murazvo-unodzora, isingaite-magnetic insulation, mavara akajeka, uye m
... 
ra, inodzivirira, isingabatike uye isiri-magnetic.
4) Impact kuramba, kwete nyore kuumbika, uye kuderedza kuneta.
5) Iyo dhizaini yakasimba, saizi inochinjika uye dzakasiyana, uye saizi yakagadzikana.
6) Anti-skid ine kusimba kushoma, inowedzera nyaradzo uye inovandudza kugona kwebasa.
7) Yakanaka uye iri nyore kuchengeta.
Iyo FRP yakaumbwa grille inogadzirwa nekusanganisa iyo pendi yekunamatira mune rese resin. Ruvara rwacho rwakasiyana, iwo ruvara rwakafanana, ruvara rwacho rwakajeka, hazvisi 
...
0-40% yekarbon simbi. Nokuraramisa mutengo FRP nesefa anenge zero. Iyo simbi nesefa inoda kuchengetedzwa gore rega rega, uye iyo yakaunganidzwa yekugadzirisa mutengo inodarika kwazvo mutengo wese weiyo FRP grid. Kunyange zvazvo kwokutanga inivhesitimendi mutengo FRP nesefa iri zvishoma kupfuura uyo wesimbi nesefa, zvachose zvoupfumi kubatsirwa iri 4-5 nguva kuti simbi nesefa. Ichi zvakare chimwe chezvikonzero zvikuru zvekushandisa kukuru-kweiyo FRP grating kunze kwenyika.

Dzimwe nyanzvi dzinofunga kuti yazvino modhi yezvisingagumi zvemukati wemubhadharo wakadzika uyeyave kuda kupera. Zvikonzero zvacho zvakasiyana.
Kune rangu divi, ndakagumisa izvozvo izvo zvandakapedza 
...

Sokunge kuti izvo zvaive zvisina kukwana, mapuratifomu matsva ari kuwedzerwa, ari emakambani akasiyana ekugadzira. Isu tinogona kupedzisira tabhadhara mapuratifomu mashanu kuti titarise pamazana gumi muzana ezve kwavo.

OBS Studio
Kana iwe unoda kuchengetedza vhidhiyo kubva kune saiti isingabvumidze kurodha pasi, tinogona kushandisa chisimba. OBS Studio inotibvumidza kutora vhidhiyo inotora ye desktop, windows uye multimedia players. Ehe iwe unofanirwa kuve uripo kuti utange kurekodha.
OBS Studio inowanikwa mu Flatpak y Snap. Mukuwedzera kune mabhinari eWindows uye Mac.

Yakakwira simba fizikisi Instutite Research Chirongwa
Ndiani akashanda naKinheng?
Munda wesimba repamusoro fizikisi inotungamirwa nevatyairi vesainzi vakapindirana kuti vaongorore zvekutanga zvinoumba nyaya nesimba, kudyidzana kuri pakati pavo, uye chimiro chenzvimbo nenguva.Hofisi yeHigh Energy Physics (HEP) inoita basa rayo kuburikidza nechirongwa chinosimudzira miganhu mitatu yekuyedza kuwanikwa kwesainzi uye kuyedza kwakabatana mudzidziso uye komputa.HEP inogadzira nyowani accelerator, detector uye computational maturusi ekugonesa sainzi, uye kuburikidza neAccelerator Stewardship inoshanda kuita kuti tekinoroji yekumhanyisa iwanikwe kune sainzi neindasitiri.
Chii chakapihwa naKinheng kuInstitute lab?
Takapa CRYSTALS zvinhu kune aya epasi rose lab kuti ashandise muAccelerator Research Program, Partical beems, DOI imaging, kuona kwenyukireya.Tinofara zvikuru kushanda navo munguva yakapfuura.isu tichaenderera mberi nekugadzira uye nekupa zvinhu zvepamberi kune aya ane mukurumbira lab.

Kanzuru yeguta reHarare inoti neMuvhuro iri kuparura chirongwa chekuchenesa guta icho chichaona musi weChishanu wekupedzisira mumwedzi wega wega uchisendekwa parutivi sezuva rekuchenesa guta.
Mutauriri wekanzuru yeHarare, VaMichael Chideme, vanoti kanzuru yatora danho iri kuitira kupa mukana kuvagari vese pamwe nevemabhizimusi kuti vaitewo bandiko ravo mukudzosera guta reHarare pambiri yaro yekare yekuve guta rinobwinya, kana kuti “Sun Shine City”.
VaChideme vanoti kuburikidza nechirongwa ichi, vagari pamwe nevashandi mumakambani akasiyanasiyana vanenge vachitarisirwa kubata mitsvairo pazuva iri vachichenesa misha yavo pamwe nenzvimbo dzavanogara, vachitiwo kanzuru yavo ichaonawo kuti yatakura marara ose anenge aunganidzwa nevanhu munzvimbo dzavo.
Guta reKigali rekuRwanda rine mukurumbira wekuve guta rakachenesesa muAfrica yose kuburikidza nechirongwa chakaparurwa nenyika iyi muna 2009 chinonzi “Umuganda.”
Chirongwa ichi chinonzi chinomanikidza zvizvarwa zvenyika iyi, kusanganisira mutungamiri wenyika nemakurukota ake, kuchenesa nzvimbo dzavagere musi weMugovera wekupedzisira mumwedzi woga woga.

Pese pandinotaura nezvazvo Shutter Ini ndinotanga nekutaura kuti ini ndashandisa chirongwa ichi uye kuti ndinochida nekuda kwemupepeti wadzo. Icho chaicho kutora skrini, asi mupepeti waro anotibvumidza isu kuvhura mifananidzo kubva ku hard drive yedu uye "kumaka" ivo kubva pairi. Nezvikonzero zvekuchengeteka, kutsamira kwakange kusisina kutsigirwa, masystem akaita seCanonical akaibvisa kubva kumahofisi avo epamutemo, saka waifanira kutendeukira kune vamwe kukwanisa kuiisa muUbuntu uye zvigadzirw
... 
rasikirwa nemhepo nekuda kwedambudziko iro, chave nacho yakawanikwa munzvimbo yepamutemo yekuchengetera, asi mukuru weprojekiti. Kunge tinokuudza mwedzi mishoma yapfuura, shanduko dzichangoburwa dzinokutendera iwe kuti udzokere kuzvinyorwa zveCanonical, asi ichi chinhu chisati chaitika izvozvi.
Iyo yakazara vhezheni yeShutter inowanikwa mune yayo yega PPA
Kugona kuisa Shutter 0.97 muUbuntu uye zvigadzirwa, ingovhura terminal uye nyora zvinotevera:
sudo add-apt-repository ppa:shutter/ppa sudo apt
...
ani inosimudzira iyo sisitimu yekushandisa ndiyo iri kuseri kweiyo Snap mapakeji. Zvichida nekuda kwechikonzero ichocho haasati adzoka. Shutter 0.97 inowanikwa mune yepamutemo Arch Linux repositories (nharaunda), saka hapana dambudziko nesoftware.
Kune avo vasina chavanoziva nezve Shutter, chishandiso chekutora skrini izvo yakatsiviwa neFlameshot pane mamwe masisitimu. Izvo hazvina kuvandudzwa munguva uye zvainge zvoda kufa, asi zvadzoka zviri zvipenyu kupfuura nakare kose.

Chikwata chenyika chemutambo wenetball chemaGems chiri kunanga kuSouth Africa kumakwikwi e 2019 Africa Netball Championships.
Chikwata ichi chiri kusimuka neChina chakananga kuCape Town, South Africa, kumakundano e2019 Africa Netball Championships ayo ari kutanga musi was 18 kusvika 23 Gumiguru.
Aive kaputeni wechikwata ichi kuWorld Cup, Perpetua Siyachitema, akaenda kuzororo, nzvimbo yake ichitorwa naFelistu Kwangwa uyo ari kutarisira mashiripiti zvekare kumaAfrica Championships aya.
Kwangwa ari kuvimbisa vatsigiri vechikwata ichi huchi nemukaka achiti iye kunyange hazvo South Africa ichiwanzo varemera, chinangwa chavo kudzoka kumba nemukombe uyu.
Zvikwata zvisere ndizvo zviri kusangana kumakundano aya, asi Zimbabwe iri kutarisira hondo yakasimba kubva kuSouth Africa, Malawi neUganda, idzo dzakakwikwidzawo zvine mutsindo Ku 2019 World Cup.
Zimbabwe iri mugungano reGroup A pamwe chete neUganda, Kenya neTanzania.
South Africa, Malawi, Zambia neLesotho dziri muGroup B.
Murairidzi wechikwata ichi, Ropafadzo Mutsauki, anoti vari kutarisira kubuda zvakanaka kumakundano aya sezvo chikwata chake chakabatana.
MaGems akasimudza pasi rese kuma 2019 World Cup kuLiverpool, England, uko vakapedza vari pachinhanho chechisere mu World Cup yavo yekutanga.
Zvichitevera zvavakaita kuLiverpool, vateveri vemutambo uyu muZimbabwe vari kuda mukombe wemuAfrica uyu.

Iyo yekuchengetedza yemahara turbine mota inokodzera 24/7 inoenderera basa.
Iwo akanakira kubatanidzwa mumashini ekugadzira, ekushandisa mukumisikidzwa kwakagadziriswa etc.

Zvese zveEletroniki zvikamu Schneider.
Industrial vacuum yekuunganidza zvakachengeteka midhiya inorema sejecha, machipisi, uye huwandu hukuru hweguruva netsvina.

VANHUKADZI vokurudzirwa kuti vapinde munyaya dzehutungamiriri hwemitambo yakasiyana-siyana kwete kutyira kure vachiti ndezvevarume chete.
Kurudziro iyi yakaitwa nachamangwiza weAmor Sports Consultancy Joyce Kapota uyo anove mudzimai ari kusimukira zvikuru munyika panyaya dzekutungamira zvemitambo.
Kapota vazhinji vanomuziva panguva yaakamboshanda kuCAPS United ari mutauriri wechikwata ichi.
Achibva kuchikwata ichi, akashanda mabasa akasiyana panguva iyo kune rimwe divi aiend
... 
i yasvika nguva yekuti madzimai achitanga kurakidzawo kuti anogona uye anokwanisa kutungamira mitambo yakasiyana sezvinoitwa nevanhurume.
“Hapana chinombotitadzisa kuti isu madzimai tibate zvigaro zvikuru mumitambo mikuru yemunyika. Saka ini ndiri kutorwirawo kodzero dzevanhukadzi kuti tiwanikwe tichitungamira mitambo yakasiyana.
“Varipo mamwe madzimai vane zvigaro mune mumitambo yakasiyana, saka tikawanda izwi redu rinoita simba uye zvinotibatsira pakuronga mitambo yakasiyana,” anodaro Kapota.

...
o yakasiyana kubatanidza vanhu.
“Sekuziva kwedu tose, mitambo inobatanidza vanhu vanobva kwakasiyana uye vemazera akasiyana. Saka isu sesangano chinangwa chedu kuti mitambo iyi tiisvitse kumatunhu akasiyana, tidzidzise vanhu kuti mitambo inokosha uye unogona kurarama nayo.
“Kune dzimwe nyika, vanhu vari kurarama nemitambo yakasiyana vachigara zvakanaka chaizvo. Saka isu chinangwa chedu kuti zvimwe chetewo izvi zviitike munyika ino yedu. Ndizvo zvimwe zvezvinangwa zveAmor Sports,” anodaro Kapota.

Chii chinonzi de minimis kukosha uye izvi zvinokanganisa sei mitero yekutakura yepasi rese?
De minimis kukosha ndicho chikumbaridzo chinosunungura kupinzwa kubva pabasa uye kana mutero / VAT, uye inosiyana nenyika. Izvi zvinogona kuve nemhedzisiro pamutero wekutumira pasi nekuti mari yekubhadharisa (iyo fizi yatinobhadhara kuva neFedEx yekubhadharisa tsika nemitero) inongobaya chete kana iyo de minimis kukosha kwapfuurwa.
Mari yemubhadharo yatinobhadhara i $ 10. Hatipfuure nemhosva iyi kwauri. S
... 
bhadhara.
Nyika dziri nhengo yeEuropean Union uye dzinoshandisa iyo Euro semari vese vanogovana zvakafanana de minimis zvikumbaridzo.
- Ose maviri basa uye VAT haibvisirwe kana inosvika 22 EUR.
- VAT asi kwete basa ichaongororwa kana iri pakati pe22 ne150 EUR.
- Ose basa uye VAT inofanirwa kana ichidarika 150 EUR.
MuUnited States, kupinza kunze kunoshanda uye hakubhadharisi mutero nekuda kwerupo $ 800 USD de minimis. Zvakare, kune dzimwe nyika uko iyo de minimis isiri yakatwasuka sezvazvinoratid
...
iwe unofanirwa kunyoresa / kuregera GST uye kwete kuburikidza neiyo tsika yekubvumidza tsika. Russia's de minimis chikumbaridzo chakanangana neumwe neumwe mutengesi muRussia, sezvo ivo vachigona chete kuendesa kusvika ku31 kilos uye kusvika ku1,000 EUR pamwedzi.
Ruzhinji rwekunze nyika dzine de minimis huwandu hwebasa nemutero. Iwe unogona kubaya yakatenderera mureza icon pane yakaderera kuruboshwe saizi yewebhu peji kana iwe uchida kuona kuti yako odha kukosha kunokanganisa sei mabasa nemitero.

“Mwanakomana Wemunhu”
ANOWANIKA KANOPFUURA KA90
Ezekieri anodanwa achinzi “mwanakomana wemunhu” kanopfuura ka90. (Ezek. 2:1) Paanoita izvi, Jehovha anenge achimuyeuchidza kuti kunyange zvazvo akapiwa basa rinokosha, angoriwo munhu wenyama. Sezvineiwo, mumabhuku eBhaibheri anotaura nezveupenyu hwaJesu, Jesu anonzi “mwanakomana wemunhu” kanenge ka80, kuratidza kuti akava munhu chaiye, kwete ngirozi yakanga yakapfeka muviri wenyama.—Mat. 8:20.
‘. . . Vachaziva Kuti Ndini Jehovha’
ANOWANIKA KANOPFUURA KA50
Kanopfuura ka50, Ezekieri akanyora mashoko aMwari ekuti vanhu ‘vachaziva kuti ndini Jehovha,’ achiratidza kuti Jehovha chete ndiye akakodzera kugamuchira kunamata kwakachena.—Ezek. 6:7.

Meya weBulawayo VaDavid Coltart vanoti guta ravo rakasarudzwa pakati pemamwe maguta emuAfrica kuti ribatsirwe nemari kubva kuhomwe yeAfrican Mayors Leadership Institute inotsigirwa neimwe shoroma yekuAm,Erica uye vaive meya weNew York VaMike Bloomberg.
Mari iyi iri muchirongwa chekusimudzira vechidiki munyaya dzekushanduka kwemamiriro ekunze kana kuti Bloomberg Philanthropies Youth Climate Action Fund.
Vachinyora padandemutande ravo reX, VaColtart vati vachashandisa mari iyi kuita zvirongwa zvekukurudzira vana vezvikoro kuti vaite zvidzidzo zvekuchenesa guta iri nekunonga maplastics anokanganisa zvakawanda.
Mamwe maguta asrudzwa muAfrica anosanganisira Accra-Ghana, Freetown-Sierra Leone, Lusaka Zambia, Nansana ne Masaka kuUganda, Quelimane kuMozambique uye Zanzibar-Tanzania.

Zimbabwe National Statistics Agency, Zimstat, yakazivisa neMuvhuro kuti kukwira kwemitengo yezvinhu kana kuti inflation yepagore mumwedzi waNdira gore rino yakakwira kuenda pazvikamu makumi matatu nezvina zvine zviga zvisere kubva muzana, kana kuti 34.8 percent, ichibva pazvikamu makumi maviri nezvitanhatu nezviga zvishanu kubva muzana, kana kuti 26.5 percent, muna Zvita wegore rapera.
Inflation yepamwedzi yakakwirawo kusvika pazvikamu zvitanhatu nezviga zvitanhatu kubva muzana, 6.6 percent muna
... 
mune zvehupfumi vachishanda vari kuBritain, Muzvare Chenaimwoyo Mutambasere, vanotiwo dambudziko riri pakuti nzira yave kushandiswa neZimstat kupima inflation, yeBlended Inflation iyi, hainzwisiswi nevakawanda.
Munyori mukuku werimwe sangano rinomirira vashandi, reZimbabwe Congress of Trade Unions, VaJaphet Moyo, vanoti kusagadzikana kwehupfumi hwenyika pasina matanho anooneka ari kutorwa nehurumende ndiko kuri kukonzera kukwira kwemitengo yezvinhu uku.
Nyanzvi mune zvehupfumi vari chipangamazan
...
utaura kuti chii chakasungwa mumusangano uyu.
Kukwira kwe inflation kuri kuuya panguva iyo dhora remunyika richinzi ratonyanya kushaya simba kana richienzaniswa nedhora rekuAmerica.
Dhora rekuAmerica rinonzi rave kunetsa kuwana izvo zvoita kuti mutengo waro ukwire, zvikuru pamusika mutema, apo rinonzi riri kutengwa nemadhora emunyika zviuru gumi nezvinomwe kana kutodarika.
Hurumende yakawedzera nguva yekuti dhora rekuAmerica rishandiswe pamwechete nedhora remunyika kusvika muna Zvita 2030.

Chitunha
Chitunha kana chibvumba (corpse in English) zvinoreva mutumbi wemunhu akafa. Chitunha chinochengetwa munzvimbo inotonhora kuti chisashata kusvika panguva yokuvigwa. Kumamisha kusina zvipatara vanhu vanoda kukasika kuviga munhu afa; vazhinji vanoviga nezuva rechitatu mushure mokunge munhu afa.
Mamwe Mazwi[chinja | edit source]
- Mhini kana chimhini (Body of murdered person), semuenzaniso, Padzivo pakaitwa mhini: someone was killed at the fight.
- Akaona mhini yomunhu: he saw the corpse of a murdered person.
- Kuviga, kana kutsira (to bury the dead) apa kureva kuradzika kana kufushira mufi murinda.
- Isau naJakobe vakororo vake vakamutsira: his sons Esau and Jacob buried him. (Genesis 35:29 Bhaibheri reChiNdau).

Der Accelerated-Mobile-Pages (AMP) Generator zum Google-AMP Seiten erstellen, die AMP-Plugins und der AMPHTML-Tag-Generator unterstützen die automatisierte Erstellung eines AMP-Carousels.
Iyo AMP carousel inotsvedza inogadzirwa otomatiki kubva pamifananidzo yese iri muchinyorwa chinyorwa nzvimbo (mune 'itemprop = chinyorwaBody' nzvimbo ).
Iyo Inokurumidza Mapeji eMapeji jenareta inogadzira otomatiki AMP carousel ichishandisa iyo 'amp-carousel' tag kana paine inopfuura imwe chinyorwa chinyorwa munzvimbo yechinyorwa!
Iyo AMP carousel inotsiva yakajairika chinyorwa chemufananidzo pane iyo AMPHTML peji.
Kana paine chifananidzo chimwe chete kana kusava nemufananidzo zvachose muchinyorwa, iyo AMP carousel yakavanzwa kuitira kuti ivandudze iyo webhusaiti nguva yekukanda, nekuti mune iyi AMP carousel JavaScript haifanirwe kutanga yatakurwa.
Panzvimbo pe AMP carousel, chete chinyorwa chinyorwa chinyorwa chinoratidzwa kana nzvimbo yacho inongoramba isina chinhu.
Mifananidzo iri muAMP carousel inopihwa nekinyorwa. Iyo   tag hunhu 'alt =' uye 'title =' inotorwa kubva papeji rekutanga semagwaro. Kana hunhu uhwu husina kutsanangurwa mune yekutanga peji, iyo Inokurumidza Mapeji eMapeji jenareta inoshandisa iyo   tag yechinyorwa.

Kocoa-yakafuma chokoreti yakasviba inogona kupihwa vanhu vane chiropa cirrhosis mune ramangwana, zvichibva pakutsvagurudza kwazvino kwakaratidza izvo zvingangove zvehutano zvinounza izvozvi padanho iri.
Vatsvagurudzo veSpain vakati kunwa chokoreti yakasviba mushure mekudya kwaizodzora kuwanda kweropa mudumbu, iro rinogona kusvika pamwero une njodzi muvarwere vecirrhotic uye muzviitiko zvakakomba kunotungamira mukuparara kwemitsipa yeropa.
Iyo antioxidants inonzi flavanols iripo mucocoa inofungidzirwa kuti ndicho chikonzero nei chokoreti yakanakira BP, sezvo aya makemikari anobatsira kutsetseka maseru emasumbu nekuita kuti mitsipa yeropa izorodze uye iwedzere, nokudaro ichideredza BP.
Chidzidzo ichi chinoratidza kushamwaridzana kuri pachena pakati pekoreti yakasviba yekushandisa uye yakadzika hypertension, ichiratidza kukosha kwekukwirisa kwevarwere vecirrhotic, "akadaro. Maka Alz, Muzvinafundo weHepatology kuImperial College London.

Hudaviri
Pakushanda kunoita zvirongwa nemabasa muhushangazhi, hudaviri (responsibility) ishoko rinodudza uyo anotarisirwa kunge achibvunzwa maererano nekufambiswa kwezvirongwa nemabsa panzvimbo iri kutaurwa nezvayo. Iye mudaviri anokwanisa kunge asiriye anobata zvombo kuita mabasa anofanirwa kuitwa asi ndiye ane chinhanho chekuronga kuti mari nezvombo zvose zvinodiwa kuti basa ribudirire zvivepo.
Munhu ane hudaviri pamusoro pekufambiswa kwezvirongwa nemabasa anofanirwa kunge akapiwa simba rehutongi pamusoro pezvinhu izvi. Kana munhu achinge asina kupiwa hutongi hazvina kufanira kuti ange ariye anobvunzwa pamusoro pekukundika kana kubudirira kwezvirongwa kana mabasa.

WASHINGTON —
Kambani yeZESA Holdings yanzi nedare ibhadhare mari inosvika zviuru gumi nezvishanu kuripa mumwe mudzimai, Amai Constance Sinachinga, vane mwanakomana akashaya mushure mekunge agwinhwa nemagetsi zvichikonzerwa nekukundikana kwevashandi vekambani iyi kuita basa nemazvo.
Takudzwa Nyandoro uyo ainge aine makore masere akaurayiwa nemagetsi musi wa 29 Kurume 2012.
Amai Sinachinga vakakwira kudare vachiti vaida mari inosvika zviuru mazana mashanu.
Asi mutomgo wedare repamusoro reHigh Court, Justice Jester Helena Charewa, vakazodzikisa mari iyi.
Amai Sinachinga vanoti kubva zvafa mwana wavo vave kurwara nechirwere cheBP, uye vave kutadza kudya.
Vanotiwo vakamanikidzwa kubva kumba kwakafira mwana wavo kuEastlea sezvo vainge voramba vachirangarira nezvekufa kwemwana wavo.
Gweta raAmai Sinachinga, Muzvare Belinda Chinowawa, avo vanoshanda nesangano reZimbabwe Lawyers for Human Rights, vanoti mutongo uyu wakakosha zvikuru panyaya yekuremekedzwa kwekodzero dzevanhu munyika.

CHIKWATA cheBeach Volleyball chenyika chevakomana muboka reUnder-21 chiri kutarisirwa kuenda kuCyprus uko chichanokwikwidza kumutambo weWorld Under-21 Beach Volleyball Championship.
Mutambo uyu uchatanga musi waChikunguru 23 kusvika 27 uine zvikwata zvakawanda zvichabva kunyika dzakasiyana.
Chikwata cheZimbabwe ndechevakomana vaviri vanoti Keith Emmerson Machakaire anodzidza paChurchill Boys High naDouglas Rufaro Choto uyo aidzidza paCornway College uye murairidzi wavo ndiNyashadzashe Takawira.
Vakomana vaviri ava parizvino vari kuita gadziriro dzavo paMachipisa Grounds apo vanosangana pakupera kwesvondo rega-rega.
Nhengo yeZimbabwe Volleyball Association, Sibanga Mashasha, anoti vatambi vaviri ava vari kuvapa rutsigirwo rwakakwana kuti vagoenda kuCyprus kunohwina mutambo uyu.
Anoti vatambi ava vane tarenda rinodadisa zvikuru.
“Chikwata chedu ichi tiri kuda chaizvo kuti chiende kuCyprus chinohwina mwedzi uno uko kuchange kuchitambirwa mutambo weU-21 World Beach Volleyball World Championship.
“Zvakakosha chaizvo kuti vanohwina sezvo zvichibatsira kusimudza mureza wenyika yedu.
“Parizvino vari kuita gadziriro dzavo svondo rega-rega apo vanosangana kwaMachipisa Grounds uko kunotambirwa mutambo webeach volleyball.

Ce: YAG kristalli yakakosha mhando yemakristani ekutsvedza. Inofananidzwa nezvimwe zvisingaenzaniswi scintillators, Ce: YAG kristaro inobata yakanyanya kupenya kushanda uye yakafara mwenje kupomba. Kunyanya, kukwirisa kwayo kukwirira i550nm, inoenderana chaizvo neiyo sensitivity kuona wavelength yesilicon photodiode kuona. Nekudaro, inokodzera kwazvo iwo scintillators emidziyo iyo yakatora iyo photodiode sema detectors uye iyo scintillators kuti vaone mwenje wakapihwa ma particles. Panguva ino, kugona kukuru kwekubatanidza kunogona kuwanikwa. Uyezve, Ce: YAG inogona zvakare kushandiswa kazhinji se phosphor mu cathode ray machubhu uye chena mwenje-inoburitsa diode.

Yakakwirira yekubatanidza kushanda pamwe nesilicon photodiode kuona

Tether yakapa $ 1 bhiriyoni mune itsva USDT tokens paTron blockchain, budiriro inofambirana nekukwira kuri kuita stablecoin musika capitalization. The kutengeserana, rakapedzwa 24 July, akacherekedzwa blockchain analytics yakasimba Arkham uye haana kupinza chero kutengeserana muripo, kufamba kazhinji vaiona sezvo bullish ari cryptocurrency nzvimbo.
Kuburitswa uku kunouya pakati pemaitiro akawedzera ekuwedzera kutenderera kwe stablecoin, kunyanya kubva June 29, maererano neemail kubva kunhengo yechikwata cheNansen kuenda ku crypto.news. Pasinei nekuwanda kwekupa, nyanzvi dzeNansen dzinonyevera pamusoro pekududzira izvi sechiratidzo chakananga chekuwedzera kwemutengo.
"Tichifunga nezvezvinhu zvakasiyana-siyana zviri kuitika muna Gumiguru 2023 uye zvino, zvinonetsa kutaura kuti mitengo inogona kuitika chete nekuwedzera uku," muongorori weNansen akadaro. Vakasimbisa kukosha kwekutarisa pa-cheni decentralized exchange mavhoriyamu, kero nhamba, uye off-cheni data senge exchange-traded homwe inoyerera, macroeconomic maonero, uye mitemo yemari.
Musika wekristptocurrency wese hausati waratidza zviratidzo zvakajeka zvekukwira kwemutengo wakakosha, kunyangwe iyo stablecoin musika chivharo yakapfuura $160 miriyoni mushure menguva yekumira. Kutenderera kuri kukura kwemastablecoins, kusanganisira Tether's USDT, Circle's USDC, Maker's DAI, Paxos' PYUSD, uye USDD, inoratidza kushanduka kuri kudiwa nemushandisi.

Vatsigiri venhabvu vari kufara nemakwikwi e2019 Africa Cup of Nations zvichitevera kuiswa kwechikwata che Zimbabwe Warriors mugungano rine nyika ina dzinoti Egypt, Democratic Republic of Congo, neUganda, vachiti gungano iri rakapfava pane remakore apfuura.
Mumubatanidzwa yezvikwata yakaitwa neveConfederation of Zimbabwe nezvikwata izvi iri muGroup A, umo vatsigiri venhabvu munyika vanoti chikwata chavo chinobudamo zvisina kutamburira.
Zvikwata zviviri zvichapedza zviri pamusoro-soro mugungano iri, nezvikwata zvina zvichapedza zviri pachinhanho chechitatu zviri nani pamagungo ese matanhatu, ndizvo zvinoenderera mberi nemakwikwi aya.
Aimbove mubati wepembe muPremier Soccer League, VaSam Hamandawana, vanoti Zimbabwe ichabudirira muGroup A.
VaShabani Muswera avo vaimbotambira Black Rhinos muSuper League vanotiwo vari kufara negungano raiswa Zimbabwe.
Mutambi wekarati ane mukurumbira asi achitevera mutambo wenhabvu, Afonso Mukuche, anoti Egypt inonetsa kurova nenyaya yevabati vepembe asi vachiyambira maWarriors kuti asadherere Uganda.
Zimbabwe yaenda kumafainari eAfrica Cup of Nations katatu muna 2004, 2006, na 2017 asi panguva yese iyi maWarriors anga achingobuditswa munharaunda yekutanga.
Asi VaHamandawana vanoti iko zvino maWarriors anobudirira asi vachiti ivo kuti izvi zviitike, panoda gadziriro yakasimba.
Makundano aya ari kutanga musi wa 21 Chikumi, Egypt neZimbabwe dzichivhura musangano wezvikwata makumi maviri nezvina aya.

Mutungamiri wehurumende uye vari mutungamiri werimwe bato reMDC, VaMorgan Tsvangirai, vanoti mutungamiri wenyika, uye vari mutungamiri weZanu PF, VaRobert Mugabe, havana masimba vari voga muhurumende yemubatanidzwa.
VaTsvangirai, avo vakataura mashoko aya kuvatori venhau muHarare neChipiri, vanoti hupenyu hwehurumende yemubatanidzwa hahuna kubatwa nemunhu mumwe chete, asi kuti nechibvumirano cheGlobal Political Agreement, icho chakanyoreranwa muna Kukadzi wegore rapera pakati pemapato matatu.
Asi chibvumirano ichi chinotiwo kana mumwe wemapato matatu aya akafunga kubuda machiri, muchato unobva wangoparara. VaMugabe vakazivisa kuti kana makore maviri angokwana, havasi kuzowedzera hupenyu hwehurumende iyi.
Vatungamiri vaviri ava vakatotanga kare kushambadza nezvesarudzo kuvatsigiri vavo, kunyange hazvo bato reMDC inotungamirirwa naVaArthur Mutambara riri kuti sarudzo hadzifanirwe kuitwa kudzamara munyika magadzikana.
Mutauriri waVaTsvangirai, VaLuke Tamborinyoka, vaudza Studio7 kuti zviri kutaurwa naVaTsvangirai ndezvekuti munhu mumwe chete muhurumende yemubatanidzwa haakwanisi kupa zuva resarudzo sezviri kuitwa naVaMugabe.
Hatina kukwanisa kubata mutauriri weZanu PF, VaRugare Gumbo, kuti tinzwewo zvinobva kubato ravo pamusoro penyaya iyi sezvo vanga vari mumusangano wePolitiburo yebato ravo.

PS UNITED – LIoyd Chitembwe – akati chikwata chake chicharwa zvakasimba kuchengetedza mukombe wePSL uyo chakahwinha mwaka wadarika.
Chitembwe anoti havasi kuvhunduka nekutungamira kuri kuitwa palog nezvikwata zvakaita seNgezi Platinum achiti kutungamira kwetarakita.
“Ligi richangotanga saka hatingatange kutaura zvekuhwinha mukombe wePSL nekuti tichangotanga. Isi tinoziva zvatiri kushandira mwaka uno, takahwinha gore radarika izvo zviri kutituma kuti tirambe tichishanda nesimba mwaka uno tihwinhe

kuti tigohwina mukombe,” anodaro.

Iye zvino, unogona kutenga salvia miltiorrihiza zvekutengesa mune chero chemishonga, mishonga yemakwenzi kana chitoro chekudya chaicho muchimiro chemakwenzi ekugadzira infusions yekumba kana muchimiro chemishonga, maoiri, zvigadzirwa, macapsule, mapiritsi kana manyuchi pakati pezvimwe zvinhu.
Mamwe mabhenefiti esalvia miltiorrihiza:
> Ichakubatsira iwe kurwisa glaucoma.
> Ichakubatsira iwe kudzikisa cholesterol yako.
> Ichakubatsira iwe kurwisa zvakanyanya pancreatitis.
> Ichakubatsira iwe kuonda.
> Ichakubatsira iwe kurwisa mamwe marudzi e bronchitis.
> Ichakubatsira iwe kumhanyisa kupisa kupisa kurapwa.

Svondo rino muchirongwa chedu ‘Hupenyu Hwedu’, tiri kutarisa nezvemabasa akanaka ari kuitwa nesangano reFrontline Zimbabwe, iro riri kubatsira vari pamberi mukurwisana pamwe nekudzvirira kupararira kwechirwere cheCovid-19 kuguta reHarare.
Imwe nhengo yeSangano iri, Muzvare Chipo Mashingaidze, vanoti sangano ravo riri kubatsira vanamukoti, vanachiremba, mapurisa, mauto pamwe nevashandi vekanzuru vari kushanda mumabasa akasiyanasiyana ane chekuita nekudzivirira chirwere charura pasi rose ichi kuburikidza nekuvatsvagira zvikwanisiro zvekupfeka vachiita mabasa avo ekurwisana neCovid-19.
Muzvare Mashingaidze vanoti vari kuunganidzawo rubatsiro rwakasiyanasiyana rwunosanganisira mvura yekunwa pamwe nezvekudya.
Vanoti sesangano, vari kubatsirawo zvakare vakwegura, vakaremara nevana vadiki vari kutungamira dzimhuri, uye vanoti kusvika pari zvino vabatsira mhuri dziri mumisha yeMbare neEpworth.
Muzvare Mashingaidze vanoti sesangano vanotenda zvikuru vose vari kubatsira nenzira dzakasiyanasiyana kuti basa ravo rirambe richienderera mberi.
Vanoti sangano ravo rakatangwa nevagari vakangozvipirawo kuti vabatsire mushure mekuona zviri kuitwa nevari kuzvipira kushanda vachidzivirira vana veZimbabwe kuti vasabatwa nechirwere ichi.
